<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3152895" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U"><link href="text/shared/02/12130000.xhp" name="Data source as table">Data source as table</link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3163829" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG"><ahelp hid=".uno:ViewFormAsGrid">Activates an additional table view when in the form view.</ahelp> When the <emph>Data source as table</emph> function is activated, you see the table in an area above the form.</paragraph>
</section>
